      "id": "PopularPost171523",
      "post_content": "If you have multiple of these out then all trigger at the beginning of the upkeep and resolve in reverse order. This means that having odd number of these out is just the same as having only one out. Having even number of these out equals [Stasis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stasis) without an upkeep cost.",
